			<div class="content" id="post-content-2139070">
									

<p>Because it’s about time we made a list.</p>
<p><strong>For a challenge thread to be added here, they must have either one or both of the following:</strong><br />
- At least five “I’m interested” or “I’m doing this” comments/posts, from different users. A challenge should be inspirational to authors and encourage discussion!<br />
- At least one successful page on the site that resulted from the challenge. A challenge should produce good work and fun!</p>
<h3><span>Notice: this material has been ported over to the page <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/writing-challenge-list">Writing Challenge List</a>. Updates will continue on that page.</span></h3>
<p>If I’ve missed a challenge or one has recently become eligible for the list, let me (Zyn) know in comments on PM. Happy writing!</p>

