<p>Agent Drieson, this isn't the place to ask for writing prompts, this is the place to ask about Challenge Threads. Furthermore,</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Someone may give me an object and one anomalous property about it. I would then elaborate on it and write the article.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This approach actually doesn't work that well for writing SCP articles up to current standards. &quot;Object + effect&quot; is effectively something more along the lines of stuff written five or more years ago; now there's more of an emphasis on backstory and what makes an item <em>more</em> than just a thing that does a thing.</p>
<p>Furthermore, authors are encouraged to think up their own ideas. If you're <em>really</em> pressed for inspiration, consider taking a look through the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/fragments">Fragments page</a> and writing up some of the ideas there.</p>

